OL,3,CMurder probe after man in 50s found
OL,4,Cdead in river
OL,6,FPolice have begun a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation after a man's body was
OL,8,Ffound in a river in Leamington Spa.
OL,10,FThe man, who is in his 50s, was found
OL,11,Fby a member of the public in Victoria
OL,12,FPark on Wednesday morning. Officers
OL,13,Fwere called shortly before 7.45am.
OL,15,FHis death was initially treated as
OL,16,Funexplained, but a post-mortem on
OL,17,FThursday established he died from
OL,18,Finjuries "consistent with an assault",
OL,19,FWarwickshire Police said.
