CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1776510171
OL,3,CMurder probe after man in 50s found
OL,4,Cdead in river
OL,6,FWarwickshire Police are appealing for
OL,7,Fany witnesses to come forward.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Gareth Unett said:
OL,10,F"I understand this will be concerning
OL,11,Ffor the local community, but I'd like
OL,12,Fto reassure them we have a team of
OL,13,Fdetectives working to establish the
OL,14,Ffull circumstances that led to the
OL,15,Fman's death.
OL,17,F"We're carrying out a number of
OL,18,Fenquiries including checking CCTV and
OL,19,Fwill have officers in and around the
OL,20,Fpark providing reassurance. If you
OL,21,Fhave questions, please speak to them.
OL,26,@rD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1776510171
OL,3,CMurder probe after man in 50s found
OL,4,Cdead in river
OL,6,F"We'd ask anyone who saw or heard
OL,7,Fanything suspicious in the area from
OL,8,Flate Tuesday evening into Wednesday
OL,9,Fmorning to come forward and share what
OL,10,Fthey know.
OL,12,F"Finally, I'd ask people not to
OL,13,Fspeculate online as this can cause
OL,14,Funnecessary distress to the family and
OL,15,Fmay impact our investigation."
OL,17,FPolice said the man's family has been
OL,18,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,19,Fspecially-trained officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@^O]
